race.comment: The well-related WHISPERING ROGUE (10) (half to 2xG2 winner and G1 placed Whispering Brook) has placed two from two over this sprint journey and will be ready to peak now third run back from the spell. Will find this assignment easier than recent Eagle Farm efforts and looks the one they all have to run down. JOY A PLENTY (9) is one from one over this course and distance and has won when fresh before. Include from the low draw. AQUATIER (6) scored by 1.5 lengths last start at Ballina and should race on the speed. Can sneak into the finish at odds. JIMMYINTHEJUNGLE (5) second up after a fine return last start, finishing just 0.7 lengths off the winner over 1000m at Toowoomba. In the mix.
